This paper deals with the coordination of multiple autonomous vehicles, which is a topic related to multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of formal verification techniques is also relevant to systems and control (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the verification of agent code, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
